Conversely, when we downregulated CXCL1, CXCL3, CCL20, and CCL5 expression in PDAC cells (sh-Chemo) using shRNA, chemokine levels in the exosomes decreased without affecting CCT6A levels, indicating that changes in chemokine expression do
